GoldenEye:;

She looked at Tails.  "Hold on fuzzy one. If you had concentrate to 
transform, you need more help than I thought.  OK,let's start with 
the basics. Your a bot with the ability to change into an animal.
This should be a natural for you to change forms.  You should be able 
to do this without thinking about it.  You say a command and it 
happens.  Try it, say your command for changing into an animal." 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Danielle Laing <sky_duv@y...> wrote:
> "Er...transform. Right."
> 'Tails' blinked.
> "Alright...I'll concenrate..." She said to herself,
> focusing. 
> 'Concentrate...'
> Tails opened her eyes, and looked down at herself.
> "Woaw..." She said, running to catch up with
> Goldeneye.
>
